Package com.iopipe.plugin.profiler

This package contains the profiler plugin which is used to profile code executions made by user code.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ThreadStatNodeTraversal
    The thread stat and the node information all have the ability to obtain nodes according to their subnodes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MethodTracker
    This class is used to keep track of methods which have executed along with their unique identifiers.
    MethodTracker.TrackedClass
    A class which has been tracked.
    MethodTracker.TrackedMethod
    A method which has been tracked.
    ProfilerExecution
    This contains the execution state for the profile plugin.
    ProfilerPlugin
    This class provides access to the profiler plugin which is used to profile method execution.
    ThreadStat
    This contains the information for a single thread which has been profiled.
    ThreadStat.Node
    This represents a single node within the trace tree.
    TimeKeeper
    This keeps track of the various times.
    Tracker
    This class keeps track of executions which have occured.

Package com.iopipe.plugin.profiler Description

This package contains the profiler plugin which is used to profile code executions made by user code. The profiler outputs to the format which is used by VisualVM and as such can be viewed by it.

2018/02/07
